rows.label: kizunainn001_msg0001
rows.name: Rex! Let's go visit the grave!

rows.label: kizunainn001_msg0002
rows.name:
But, we only just went...
Is there something special you
wanted to do there?

rows.label: kizunainn001_msg0003
rows.name:
I just had something that I
wanted to ask your parents
about.

rows.label: kizunainn001_msg0004
rows.name:
We didn't get much time before,
so I want to talk to them
properly this time, y'know?

rows.label: kizunainn001_msg0005
rows.name:
Oh she's got a good attitude,
that one.

rows.label: kizunainn001_msg0006
rows.name:
Make sure you take good care
of her, Rex!
